scene.message:
Brown: What... what was that?!{nl}
Why did I...? What{nl}
even was that?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: You too, Brown...{nl}
But of all people, why{nl}
would it show up in him...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Awesome!!{nl}
I always knew I was{nl}
a hero of justice!{waitkey}{clearbox}Yeah, like even as a kid{nl}
I always felt I was{nl}
a little different!!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: He doesn't{nl}
quite get it...{wait_fr:32}Oh well.{waitkey}{nl}
{wait_fr:16}Anyway, {ctl0f:1},{nl}
I'm coming with you.{waitkey}You guys alone worries{nl}
me a little,{nl}
y'know?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: That's my line.{nl}
Inaba, hand the Security{nl}
Card over to {ctl0f:1}.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...Fine. Here.{nl}
"Security Card." Don't{nl}
you lose it.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Here's your gun,{nl}
Inaba. Don't go shooting{nl}
us by mistake.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey hey, mind if{nl}
I tag along?{waitkey}You guys are missing{nl}
a little star power.{nl}
With me here, the crew'll{nl}
really shine! So, {ctl08:32769}

Brown: OK!{waitkey}{nl}
I guess I'll lend you{nl}
my help! Wa ha ha ha!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Here's your gun,{nl}
Brown. Don't fire it{nl}
wildly.{waitkey}{clearbox}...What are you looking at?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Oh, is that so?{nl}
Really? No regrets?{nl}
Oh well...{waitkey}{clearbox}Guess I'll just go to school{nl}
then.{wait_fr:16}...{wait_fr:21}Don't come{nl}
crying to me later!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Alright! Now that{nl}
everyone's here...{nl}
where are we going again?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Don't lose the{nl}
Security Card.{waitkey}{clearbox}We need it to get into{nl}
the loading dock at{nl}
the old factory.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: The Inspector{nl}
turning into a demon...{nl}
total madness!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: "Let's go!"?{nl}
Or "Per-SOOOO-na!"?{nl}
Both are way too lame.{waitkey}{clearbox}How about "Right on!"{nl}
or something?!{waitkey}{ret}
